      "title": "Corona for experts",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Spinner Praveen Jayawickrama, who represents the Sri Lankan Test squad, has been diagnosed with Corona virus, says the Sri Lanka Cricket Institute.",
        "The Cricket Institute also states that the rest of the players of the Sri Lankan team have not been infected with the Corona virus."
